quran[8{c,v,t}:
35,31,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) jo kitaab hum ne tumhari taraf wahi ke zareya se bhaije hai wohi haq hai, tasdeeq karti hui aayi hai unn kitabon ki jo iss se pehlay aayi theen be shak Allah apne bundon ke haal se bakhabar hai aur har cheez par nigah rakhnay wala hai"
35,32,"phir hum ne is kitaab ka waris bana diya unn logon ko jinhein hum ne ( iss waarsat ke liye ) apne bundon mein se chunn liya ab koi to un mein se apne nafs par zulm karne wala hai, aur koi beech ki raas hai, aur koi Allah ke azan se nakiyon mein Sabqat karne wala hai, yahi bohat bara fazl hai"
35,33,"hamesha rehne wali jannaten hain jin mein yeh log daakhil hon ge wahan inhen sonay ke kanganon aur motiyon se aaraasta kya jaye ga, wahan un ka libaas resham hoga"
35,34,"aur woh kahin ge ke shukar hai uss khuda ka jis ne hum se gham daur kar diya, yaqeenan hamara rab maaf karne wala aur qader frmane wala hai"
35,35,"jis ne hamein apne fazl se abdi qiyam ki jagahtehra diya, ab yahan nah hamein koi mushaqqat paish aati hai aur nah takan la-haq hoti hai"
35,36,aur jin logon ne kufar kya hai unn ke liye jahannum ki aag hai nah unn ka qissa pak kar diya jaye ga ke mar jayen aur nah unn ke liye jahannum ke azaab mein koi kami ki jaye gi iss terhan hum badla dete hain har uss shakhs ko jo kufar karne wala ho
35,37,"woh wahan cheekh cheekh kar kahin ge ke"" ae hamaray rab, hamein yahan se nikaal le taakay hum naik amal karen unn aamaal se mukhtalif jo pehlay karte rahay thay"" ( inhen jawab diya jaye ga )"" kya hum ne tum ko itni Umar nah di thi jis mein koi sabaq lena chahta to sabaq le sakta thaا? aur tumahray paas mutnabba karne wala bhi aa chuka tha ab maza chako zaalmon ka yahan koi madadgaar nahi hai """
35,38,"be shak Allah asmano aur zameen ki har posheeda cheez se waaqif hai, woh to seenon ke chupay hue raaz taq jaanta hai"
